Class AbstractMessagesSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.ldeitos.validation.impl.interpolator.AbstractMessagesSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessagesSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultipleBundlesSource

    public abstract class AbstractMessagesSource
extends Object
implements MessagesSource
    Abstract implementation to MessagesSource.
    Provide a Pattern compiled by Constants.KEY_PATTERN, a key group index in regex pattern, a Matcher provider method and default implementation to MessagesSource.getMessage(String) and MessagesSource.getMessage(String, Locale)
    Author:
    Leandro Deitos

      • getInSource

        protected abstract String getInSource(String original,
                 String key,
                 Locale locale)
        Parameters:
        original - Original 'message' constraint attribute content.
        E.g: "{keyContent}"
        key - Key extracted from original message if that is key pattern compatible.
        E.g: "{keyContent}" or "[keyContent]" result "keyContent"
        locale - Locale to get localized message, may be null.
        Returns:
        The message obtained from message source by the key, or original 'message' content if the key does not gives any correspondent.
